This directory is a fork of https://github.com/k1p1l0/claude-telegram-supercharged
(Apache-2.0), republished in this marketplace for easier installation.

Local modifications vs upstream:
- Plugin renamed from `telegram` to `telegram-supercharged` throughout
- State directory changed from `~/.claude/channels/telegram/` to
  `~/.claude/channels/telegram-supercharged/` to avoid collisions with the
  official Telegram plugin
- Slash commands rebased under `/telegram-supercharged:*`
- `supervisor.ts` launches `--channels plugin:telegram-supercharged@blackpaw-plugins`
  instead of the upstream `plugin:telegram@claude-plugins-official`
- `skills/update/` removed — updates are pulled manually via the
  `sync-telegram-supercharged` project skill

Upstream is synced into this fork on-demand, not automatically. See
`.claude/skills/sync-telegram-supercharged/SKILL.md` at the repo root for the
procedure.

Issues about the underlying plugin belong upstream; issues about the
marketplace packaging belong here.
